long.ar,da,de,es,fr,it,ja,ko,pt_PT,ru:
Dubli SaveMate® is your FREE companion & time-saving tool for quick and easy access to deals, coupons, and Cash Back!

With the Dubli SaveMate® browser extension, you can now shop directly from your favorite store’s site and view all available deals, coupons, promo codes, free shipping offers, and applicable Cash Back rates in your browser.

Never miss a deal again by instantly seeing your Cash Back earning opportunities that you can double with coupons when you search the Web for your favorite products and/or brands. Enhance your search results by adding Dubli SaveMate® to your browser bar. You can easily deactivate the extension by simply signing out at any time; no need to uninstall. Or quickly sign back in whenever you need it.

With Dubli SaveMate®, saving and earning Cash Back has never been more convenient, faster or easier! Try it out; it’s easy and it’s FREE!
